{"tid":1202083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[呼籲]有緣見到CCTVB，大家要識做","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:25:30.000Z","uid":2156,"like":1086,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"eb13359ad9f4379fd20dfa2acfffd240a88a7af2","tid":1202083,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"唔係重點，但大家有緣見到CCTVB做直播/收音就大嗌或自製banner<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無線新聞，是是但但<br />\n袁志偉死全家</span></span><br />\n之類<br />\n<br />\n嗌咩唔係重點，齊心屌鳩TVB<br />\n目的係影響tvb收音，拍攝緊嘅畫面<br />\n過往經驗，佢做live無得cut，直上電視，但新聞時段就會cut晒呢啲畫面/收音，令佢無嘢播都好<br />\n<br />\n橫掂TVB妓者都係鳩噏<br />\n血債血償，清鳩tvb袋"},{"pid":"592e895cfbd11693fcd8aff6d40847277e2cadc0","tid":1202083,"uid":2156,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/McEgGsDElrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMcEgGsDElrE&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=ef09f697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/McEgGsDElrE</a>"},{"pid":"57d070189ecc7d1f0ba5266ad9c41767a559f0ee","tid":1202083,"uid":2156,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7wEwe-b40Ck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7wEwe-b40Ck&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=a4d0630b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7wEwe-b40Ck</a>"},{"pid":"82a1fc702386b87a2b93e8fb43afe08a5b97a02b","tid":1202083,"uid":2156,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vHCBw8ixKLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvHCBw8ixKLI&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=f96eea37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vHCBw8ixKLI</a>"},{"pid":"71ca520170d27524b20becc9809b7d329897d0af